SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT Subscription_Type_ID, Name, Options, Active FROM Subscription_Type WHERE Active = 'Y' :1 :2 ORDER BY Name

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Subscription_Type WHERE Active = 'Y' :1 :2
